= Delete Submission

- Epic: Assignment Submission
- Actor: Student
- MVP: No
- BR: BR-SUB-3
- Description / Notes: Delete a submitted assignment.
- As a: Student
- I want to: Delete my submission
- So that: I can retract it.
- Trigger: The student decides to withdraw their submission.
- Pre-condition:
    - The student has submitted the assignment.
    - The deadline has not passed (optional, depends on system rules).
- Post-condition:
    - The submission is removed.
- Solution (Step-by-Step):
  - Go to the assignment page.
  - Click "Delete Submission".
  - Confirm the deletion.
